# ==(_:_:)

**Operator**

Returns a Boolean value that indicates whether the two add secure element pass errors are equal.

## Declaration

```swift
static func == (lhs: PKAddSecureElementPassError, rhs: PKAddSecureElementPassError) -> Bool
```

## Parameters

- **lhs**: An add secure element pass error to compare.
- **rhs**: Another add secure element pass error to compare.

## Return Value

[doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/true] if the two errors are equal; otherwise, [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/swift/false].
